					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I felt so comfortable whenever we spent time together.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"跟他度过的时间比任何事物都更舒心。",
