					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"My approach angle is taking me... right into that cliff. Shit. I’ll be a stain on the wall if I stay on this course.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"这样下去会直接撞上岩盘。那样一来肯定会没命。",
